      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's not a new chapter though. i mean, i've tried to start over so many times, but the well is just dry. i feel like i'm just dragging this heavy, useless body around. even the idea of a \"new beginning\" feels like a joke when there's nothing left to build with. it just feels like the light has completely gone out. do you think it's possible to just... be done? when the purpose is gone?",
